Shar’s Birthday:&lt;br /&gt;
The birthday is October 6th, but the party will be Saturday,&lt;br /&gt;
October 5. It’s my 24th birthday and the first one in some&lt;br /&gt;
years for which I’ve been employed. Plus, I have new clothes.&lt;br /&gt;
So I have cause to celebrate. More importantly, though,&lt;br /&gt;
we’ve cleaned the house! The address is 506-D Albert Street.&lt;br /&gt;
